{"tid":852043,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)各位巴打 想請教下 想問呢啲係咩黎？","createTime":"2018-10-07T14:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T22:54:52.000Z","uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f97e7df9966894bf00d8f9150dc4330e727ef0","tid":852043,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友 隻手 ，手臂，手爭，個頭，頸後面，耳仔後面都生左呢啲一粒粒既野。<br />\n<br />\n有時會好痕，要R到流血先唔痕<br />\n試過睇醫生 醫生話係濕疹 搽過所有野 食過抗生素都係咁<br />\n有時以為佢會好啲 但又出過。<br />\n<br />\n想問下呢啲係咩疹？定牛皮廯？<br />\n洗唔洗抽指甲去染下？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有無醫生可以介紹下 <br />\n真心好困擾我朋友。 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/222333_b6a62c091da6ffdd30862096dcce7375.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F222333_b6a62c091da6ffdd30862096dcce7375.png&h=1dd7d643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/222341_4ee5ff9895fa325da8c49ff43862ac26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F222341_4ee5ff9895fa325da8c49ff43862ac26.png&h=ef5974cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1327b123c792d8d45fc7713c6a3e5e6b4e2f4bdb","tid":852043,"uid":35649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"最近有冇食過咩藥？<br />\n條脷有冇生野？"},{"pid":"9f808b6244b8931450a822375bf77fac6e12339f","tid":852043,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1327b123c792d8d45fc7713c6a3e5e6b4e2f4bdb","tid":852043,"uid":35649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"最近有冇食過咩藥？<br />\n條脷有冇生野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"條脷無生野<br />\n無食藥 。。但有食煙"},{"pid":"f42065d5104c4727a729d2f40c8d88fe8fa3d39b","tid":852043,"uid":126609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回